# Bloom Spheres in Blender using Sverchok scripted node

A scripted node and some example .blend files to produce bloom spheres similar to those described by John Edmaek in this [instructable](http://www.instructables.com/id/Blooming-Zoetrope-Sculptures/).


Further information can be found at my blog [Look Think Make](http://elfnor.com/bloom-spheres-in-sverchok.html).


![bloom sphere example](bloom_wobble.png)

